1.基本命令
mysql -u root -p
show databases;
use flask-----要用的数据库
show tables;
drop database flaskr_db_test
delete from user where username='admin1'
update operators set disabled=1 where id =2

.open flask.db
.table



2.创建数据库
create database pixie_test default charset utf8;
create user rocky identified by '11111';
grant all privileges on pixie_test.* to rocky;
flush privileges;------刷新权限相关表
drop user rock;

3.安装mysql

apt-get install mysql-server
apt-get install mysql-client
apt-get install libmysqlclient-dev

4.监听地址修改
默认是127.0.0.1，要给别人用，就得改0.0.0.0
在etc/mysql的底层cnf文件中修改
改完systemctl restart mysql

